Got done about ten minutes ago! Simple process. They have tutorial on their site. My atomizer looked different than the one on the site though so I had to look up reference in YouTube. Well it started out a bit u sure of how sensitive and delicate I need to treat things, but soon got a feel for the process. The tool of the wire cutter is useful but I found myself searching For a mini glasses screwdriver to remove the og grommet.  It was stuck in there.
